803
01:21:12.080 --> 01:21:13.165
and all that bullshit.

804
01:21:14.416 --> 01:21:17.211
But I knew Hell would be
a pretty fucking sweet place.

805
01:21:18.086 --> 01:21:19.046
Go on.

806
01:21:20.756 --> 01:21:21.965
Suit yourself.

807
01:21:22.966 --> 01:21:24.843
