812
01:21:39.900 --> 01:21:40.984
Or is it Bi-Han.

813
01:21:41.860 --> 01:21:44.320
No. I think it's Bi-Han.
That Sub-Zero fucker.

814
01:21:44.321 --> 01:21:46.864
You know. he killed your
whole family or some shit.

815
01:21:46.865 --> 01:21:48.324
